<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Avery Signal Lab — Powered by Jakoma</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Avery Signal Lab, powered by Jakoma. Filtered market intelligence for high-volatility digital assets. Private beta opening soon." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0b1020" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Avery Signal Lab — Powered by Jakoma" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Filtered signal intelligence for high-volatility digital assets." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #08111f;
      --bg-soft: #0e1b33;
      --panel: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --panel-strong: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      --text: #edf2ff;
      --muted: #b5c0de;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --accent: #79b8ff;
      --accent-2: #91f0d1;
      --warning: #ffd27a;
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      --radius: 22px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behaviour: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(121,184,255,0.18), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(145,240,209,0.12), transparent 25%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #07101f 0%, #091427 45%, #08111f 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 2rem));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(8, 17, 31, 0.78);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .brand strong {
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .brand span {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      padding: 0.95rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #9dd1ff);
      color: #07111d;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(121, 184, 255, 0.28);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-color: var(--line);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 5.5rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.45rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(145,240,209,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(145,240,209,0.18);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .hero p.lead {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 62ch;
      margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
    }

    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .hero-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .signal-panel {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.04));
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 1.4rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .panel-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .live-dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      background: var(--accent-2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(145,240,209,0.14);
    }

    .metric-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .metric-card {
      background: rgba(7,16,29,0.65);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .metric-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
    }

    .metric-top strong { font-size: 1rem; }
    .score {
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .tag-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      margin-top: 0.65rem;
    }

    .tag {
      padding: 0.35rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    section { padding: 2rem 0; }

    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .section-copy {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 70ch;
      margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.2rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .beta-box {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .list li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .list li::before {
      content: "•";
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-top: 0.05rem;
    }

    .pricing {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin: 0.45rem 0 0.2rem;
    }

    .small {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .highlight {
      border-color: rgba(121,184,255,0.35);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(121,184,255,0.14);
    }

    .faq {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.9rem;
    }

    details {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    }

    summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    details p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0.8rem 0 0;
    }

    .waitlist-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(121,184,255,0.12), rgba(145,240,209,0.08));
      border: 1px solid rgba(121,184,255,0.22);
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 1.4rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .waitlist-form {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .waitlist-form input {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(7,16,29,0.75);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
      font: inherit;
    }

    .waitlist-help {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 0.85rem;
    }

    .disclaimer {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 210, 122, 0.22);
      background: rgba(255, 210, 122, 0.08);
      color: #ffe7b1;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 1.4rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .grid-3,
      .grid-2,
      .pricing,
      .beta-box {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero { padding-top: 4.5rem; }
      .waitlist-form { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cta-row { flex-direction: column; }
      .btn { width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a href="#top" class="brand" aria-label="Avery Signal Lab home">
        <strong>Avery Signal Lab</strong>
        <span>Powered by Jakoma</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="#what">What it is</a>
        <a href="#beta">Beta</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#waitlist">Join waitlist</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Private beta opening soon</div>
          <h1>Filtered market intelligence for high-volatility digital assets.</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Avery Signal Lab helps cut through noise in fast-moving token markets by filtering, scoring and ranking live opportunities.
            It is built for people who want structured signal intelligence — not hype, not chaos, and not empty promises.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#waitlist">Join the beta waitlist</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#what">See how it works</a>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-note">
            Founder-led research beta. Powered by Jakoma. Designed to surface higher-quality setups and strip out obvious rubbish before it reaches you.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="signal-panel" aria-label="Example signal panel">
          <div class="panel-head">
            <span>Example signal view</span>
            <span style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;"><span class="live-dot"></span> Live beta</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-stack">
            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <strong>Signal A — High confidence</strong>
                <span class="score">Score 0.84</span>
              </div>
              <div>Liquidity strong. Volatility elevated. Retrace risk moderate. Candidate passed multi-stage filters.</div>
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Tier A</span>
                <span class="tag">Momentum build</span>
                <span class="tag">Filtered</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <strong>Signal B — Watchlist only</strong>
                <span class="score" style="color: var(--warning);">Score 0.67</span>
              </div>
              <div>Interesting movement, but quality gate not strong enough for top-tier alerting.</div>
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Tier B</span>
                <span class="tag">Needs confirmation</span>
                <span class="tag">Not premium feed</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <strong>Filtered out</strong>
                <span class="score" style="color:#ffaeae;">Rejected</span>
              </div>
              <div>Low liquidity, distorted structure, or weak event profile. The point is to bin bad candidates quickly.</div>
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Low liquidity</span>
                <span class="tag">Noise reduction</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="what">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">What Avery Signal Lab actually is</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">
          This is not a meme-coin megaphone and it is not positioned as personal financial advice. It is a signal intelligence beta built to scan, filter and surface structured opportunities in chaotic markets.
        </p>
        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Signal filtering</h3>
            <p>Potential setups are ranked and filtered so the feed is driven by quality thresholds rather than volume for the sake of volume.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Event-led logic</h3>
            <p>The lab is built around market-state shifts, not random token chatter. The goal is to identify clearer momentum and retrace conditions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Proof over noise</h3>
            <p>Outputs are designed to be testable, reviewable and iterated on. Beta users get early access to the engine as it hardens.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container beta-box">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);">Who this is for</h2>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>People already comfortable operating in high-volatility digital asset markets.</li>
            <li>Users who want a filtered research feed rather than random unranked calls.</li>
            <li>Early adopters happy to join a founder-led beta and help shape the product.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Who it is not for</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Beginners looking for guaranteed profits.</li>
            <li>Anyone expecting personal investment advice.</li>
            <li>People who want reckless volume instead of tighter signal quality.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="beta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Private beta structure</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">
          The first release is designed as a limited beta: controlled access, higher-touch feedback, and a smaller cohort while the engine continues to improve.
        </p>
        <div class="grid-2">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>What beta users get</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Filtered signal alerts</li>
              <li>Risk-aware commentary on why something passed or failed</li>
              <li>Weekly summary snapshots</li>
              <li>Direct exposure to an evolving engine rather than a static feed</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Why it is limited</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>To keep quality under control</li>
              <li>To refine the signal logic with real usage feedback</li>
              <li>To avoid opening the gates before the evidence base is stronger</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="pricing">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Planned pricing</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">
          The aim is to start small, test properly, and only then harden the offer. Founding beta members get the earliest access and the lightest pricing.
        </p>
        <div class="pricing">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Waitlist</h3>
            <div class="price">Free</div>
            <p class="small">Register interest and get notified when private beta spaces open.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card highlight">
            <h3>Founding Beta</h3>
            <div class="price">£29<span class="small">/month</span></div>
            <p class="small">Limited seats. Early access, filtered alerts, and direct founder updates during beta.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Core Tier</h3>
            <div class="price">Later</div>
            <p class="small">A fuller recurring offer will follow once the beta evidence base is stronger and the product is more mature.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Questions people will ask</h2>
        <div class="faq">
          <details>
            <summary>Is this financial advice?</summary>
            <p>No. Avery Signal Lab is positioned as market intelligence and research output. It is not personal financial advice, portfolio management, or a guarantee of returns.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>When does beta start?</summary>
            <p>Beta opens once the live engine and reporting chain are stable enough for controlled public access. The waitlist is the first way in.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>How are alerts delivered?</summary>
            <p>The current plan is private beta delivery via a lightweight channel such as Telegram, WhatsApp or email, depending on what is most practical and reliable.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Why not just publish everything publicly?</summary>
            <p>Because quality matters more than noise. A smaller beta lets the product improve with real feedback before being pushed wider.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="waitlist">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="waitlist-box">
          <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Join the Avery Signal Lab waitlist</h2>
          <p class="section-copy" style="margin-bottom: 0; max-width: 56ch;">
            Get first notice when private beta spaces open. This page is GitHub-friendly and static, so connect the form to your preferred provider later.
          </p>
          <form class="waitlist-form" action="mailto:hello@averysignallab.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" aria-label="Email address" required />
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request beta access</button>
          </form>
          <p class="waitlist-help">
            Tip: when you publish this, replace the mailto action with Formspree, ConvertKit, Tally, MailerLite, or a simple form endpoint.
          </p>
          <div class="disclaimer">
            Cryptoassets are high risk. Avery Signal Lab is a research-led beta and should not be relied on as personal investment advice. Nothing on this page is a promise of performance or return.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div>
          <strong>Avery Signal Lab</strong><br />
          Powered by Jakoma
        </div>
        <div>
          <a href="mailto:hello@averysignallab.com">hello@averysignallab.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
